# Claude Code Deployment System

## Overview
This system lets you use Claude Code to automatically deploy your local changes to staging with simple commands.

## Setup (One-time)

### Step 1: Create Deployment Configuration

Create a file called `claude-deployment-config.json` in your project root:

```json
{
    "staging": {
        "ftp_host": "wp20.domains.co.za",
        "ftp_user": "profirea",
        "ftp_password": "tv1+TkUY53@1Yz",
        "remote_path": "/public_html/alpha.selpro.co.za/",
        "url": "https://alpha.selpro.co.za",
        "database": {
